snippet.title: Braindead 13 - Video Game Trailer - PC MS-DOS, 1995
snippet.description:
Braindead 13 - Video Game trailer.
Developed and published (USA)  by ReadySoft Incorporated in 1995 for PC MS-DOS, then in 1996 for Windows 95 and many consoles.
Published  in Europe by Empire Interactive Entertainment.

Other versions :
1995 :
-PC MS-DOS.
1996 :
-PC Windows 95
-3DO
-Jaguar
-Macintosh
-Saturn
-Playstation
1997 :
-CD-i . Published by Philips Interactive Media. Ported by International Creative Digital Image.

Video from the Braindead 13 playable Demo. (1995)
